<br>
FnF has some pretty tough entry requirements. Yet we still get people applying and getting in. I am sure the folks in Reso are experiencing the same thing.<br>
<br>
Don't like FnF or Reso? Thats fine. Do what Awakened souls did. Start your own guild. I hear they pretty much cleared PoG last weekend. Got a nice Enchanter Robe too. Congrats you guys.<br>
<br>
There is absolutely NOTHING that prevents people from playing the high end game that YOU can't overcome if you put your mind to it. As proof, I point to the many different types of high end guilds on many different servers who's numbers range anywhere from 30 to 300. Getting to play in the high end game in EQ is no different than trying to achieve anything in life. If you want it bad enough just work hard for it.<br>
