<br>
While you are right, Kzan, about the gating here on FV and MANY other servers, that is not actually the case on some.<br>
<br>
Several uberguilds (FoH, etc) have admitted to having VI employees in their midst at one time or another. Most of these guilds have a 'blackball' policy... if ONE person dislikes you, you cannot get in.<br>
<br>
Since in the past, VI employees were members... you can see where this is a VERY sticky situation.<br>
<br>
Add to that the fact that many uberguilds have some disagreeable sorts as members (reference this thread), and you can see why I have a problem with it.<br>
<br>
Sometimes real assholes can gain the respect and ear of persons with influence... and ruin things for people they don't like.<br>
<br>
One of the biggest reasons I left my old server is because disagreeable people in my own guild were ruining the high level game for those I thought were quality people... both by keeping them out of our guild, and by smearing some of them bad enough to keep them out of other guilds. It was creating a guild of people who either WERE disagreeable (read: assholes) or were willing to let the assholes run rampant.<br>
<br>
While this doesn't happen here, I feel very strongly about disagreeable people being allowed to influence whether or not and when people experience the high level game.<br>
<br>
There is, in my opinion, no reason why one person should have to expend significantly more effort to get into the high level game. There is also no reason to have to deal with small minded people when you are playing a game for fun. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=885.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=885.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=885.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=885.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=885.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm58">Telegrams!<option value="firionaviefrm47">Guilds and Associations<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Day<option value="firionaviefrm23">Hero Heart Tavern<option value="firionaviefrm15">The Polling Booth<option value="firionaviefrm40">Kudos!<option value="firionaviefrm48">Ye Olde Coffeeshop<optio